cd6710d56b63c80501ec0e5e15991395fdab9e99:
query GetBid($bidId: String!) {
  bidByBidId(bidId: $bidId) {
    bidId
    auctionAddress
    auctionName
    bundleHash
    replacedBy
    signer
    signature
    status
    submittedTimestamp
    statusLastUpdated
    tipRevealed
    txHash
    amount
    auctionByAuctionAddressAndAuctionName {
      price
      chainId
      __typename
    }
    __typename
  }
}
